#odels.md-and-Factor-M Lesson 07: Quantitative Investing and Factor Models

## Learning Objectives

By the end of this lesson, students will be able to:
- Understand quantitative investing principles and methodologies
- Master factor investing concepts (value, growth, quality, momentum)
- Comprehend smart beta strategies and implementation
- Learn quantitative portfolio construction techniques
- Understand factor models and optimization methods
- Master backtesting and performance analysis
- Evaluate technology applications in quantitative investing
- Build systematic quantitative investment strategies

